s and The Novelist's Duty to the Truth</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">June 10, 2024</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/jennybartoy/">Jenny Bartoy</a></span></div></li><li><div class="post_circle_thumb"><a href="https://crimereads.com/vintage-horror-illustrations/"><img class="lazy" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/plugins/lb-content-widgets/img/lazy-sq.png" data-src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2024/05/horror-cover-2-150x150.jpg" alt=""></a></div><div class="text-container"><strong class="title"><a href="https://crimereads.com/vintage-horror-illustrations/">Bump In the Night: Vintage Horror Illustrations Gave Us the Shivers</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">June 10, 2024</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/keithroysdon/">Keith Roysdon</a></span></div></li><li><div class="post_circle_thumb"><a href="https://crimereads.com/southern-noir-lansdale-james-ross/"><img class="lazy" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/plugins/lb-content-widgets/img/lazy-sq.png" data-src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2024/05/they-dont-dance-much-150x150.jpg" alt=""></a></div><div class="text-container"><strong class="title"><a href="https://crimereads.com/southern-noir-lansdale-james-ross/">The Backlist: Joe R. Lansdale on a Forgotten Classic of Southern Noir</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">June 10, 2024</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/pollystewart/">Polly Stewart</a></span></div></li></ul></li>
